## Release

To make new release of application, run  
`release.bash` script.  
Set new package version and write description.

## User data directory

~/.config/pomodoro

## Environment variables

POMODORO_DEV  
Open devtools in render process - window

```
POMODORO_DEV=true
```

## Images/icons

### Electron forge - build app

Supported formats

| Operation system | Format | Size                                           |
| ---------------- | ------ | ---------------------------------------------- |
| macOS            | .icns  | 512x512 pixels (1024x1024 for Retina displays) |
| Windows          | .ico   | 256x256 pixels                                 |
| Linux            | .png   | 512x512 pixels                                 |

Configuring installer icons

https://www.electronforge.io/guides/create-and-add-icons#configuring-installer-icons

### Electron api - native-image

Supported Formats

Currently PNG and JPEG image formats are supported.  
On Windows, you can also load ICO icons from file paths.

Small icon

- 16x16 (100% DPI scale)
- 20x20 (125% DPI scale)
- 24x24 (150% DPI scale)
- 32x32 (200% DPI scale)

Large icon

- 32x32 (100% DPI scale)
- 40x40 (125% DPI scale)
- 48x48 (150% DPI scale)
- 64x64 (200% DPI scale)
- 256x256

